quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  104,4,"Rárá (kò rí bẹ́ẹ̀). Dájúdájú wọ́n máa kù ú lókò sínú Hutọmọh ni."
  104,5,"Kí sì ni ó mú ọ mọ ohun tó ń jẹ́ Hutọmọh?"
  104,6,"(Òhun ni) Iná Allāhu tí wọ́n ń kò (tó ń jó geregere),"
  105,1,"Ṣé o kò wòye sí bí Olúwa rẹ ti ṣe ọ̀rọ̀ ìjọ elérin ni?"
  105,2,"Ṣé kò sọ ète wọn di òfo àti anù bí?"
  105,3,"Ó sì rán àwọn ẹyẹ níkọ̀níkọ̀ sí wọn."